Vector Terminology used/not used

 

To improve the usability of this help, the terminology is unified.

Alternatively, or synonymously used terms are avoided.

The following lists contrast two types of terms:

  • terms that are used at Vector
  • terms that are no longer used at Vector

If you were searching for terms that are no longer used, you can find that page here and then search for the terms that are used.
